'''雷射武器系統'''（Laser Weapon System），簡稱'''LaWS'''，是一種由[[美國海軍|美國海軍]]開發的指向性能量[[激光武器|激光武器]]。此武器在2014年安裝在[[庞塞号船坞登陆舰|龐塞號]]USS Ponce (LPD-15)上測試。<ref>{{cite news|title=Navy's New Laser Weapon Blasts Bad Guys From Air, Sea|author=Luis Martinez|url=http://news.yahoo.com/navys-laser-weapon-blasts-bad-215808231.html|newspaper=[[American_Broadcasting_Company|ABC]]|date=9 Apr 2013|accessdate=9 April 2013|archive-date=2014-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140822063513/http://news.yahoo.com/navys-laser-weapon-blasts-bad-215808231.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=U.S. Navy sees shipboard laser weapon coming soon|author=Jonathan Skillings|url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-11386_3-57578559-76/u.s-navy-sees-shipboard-laser-weapon-coming-soon/|newspaper=[[CNET|CNET]]|date=8 Apr 2013|accessdate=9 April 2013|archive-date=2014-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219041542/http://news.cnet.com/8301-11386_3-57578559-76/u.s-navy-sees-shipboard-laser-weapon-coming-soon/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=US to deploy new laser weapon to Persian Gulf|url=http://rt.com/usa/us-laser-weapon-persian-gulf-530/|newspaper=[[RT_(TV_network)|Russia Today]]|date=9 April 2013|accessdate=9 April 2013|archive-date=2014-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140410192829/http://rt.com/usa/us-laser-weapon-persian-gulf-530/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

